Egg group - MINERAL / AMORPHOUS

These Pok√©mon arose from the spirits of people interred in graves in past ages. Each of them carries a mask that used to be its face when it was human.
Grave robbers who mistake them for real coffins and get too close end up trapped inside their bodies. Their bodies are covered in pure gold.
